<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <style>
        .mail-container{
            width: 100vw;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: black;
            color: #ffcff1;
            border: 2px solid red;
        }
        .header{
            width: 100%;
            height: 50px ;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-family: monospace;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffcff1;
        }
        .message-box{
            font-family: cursive;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-top: 5px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-content{
            width: 98%;
            padding: 5%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-family: monospace;
            color: #ee9b00;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
<div class="mail-container">
    <div class="header">
        <a><h1>Cloud Connect</h1></a>
    </div>

    <div class="message-box">
        "A one stop solution to fight Covid-19".
    </div>
    <div class="email-content">
        Hiiüëãüèª <%= name%><br><br>

        This is to imform you that <%= comment.user.name%> has made a comment on your
        post named "<%= comment.post.title%>" that is:<br><br>

        <font style="color: white;">
            "<%= comment.content%>".<br><br>
        </font>

        Come online to reply back&nbsp; <a href="/">Click Here</a>

    </div>
</div>
    
</body>
</html>
